Products.SmallFormatDescription: Nourishing Bubs Babies First Foods Fruit
Products.FullDescription: Nourishing Bubs Babies First Foods Fruit
Products.RichDescription:
Designed by Paedatric Dietitian and Nutritionist Olivia Bates, this Baby's First Foods Fruit pack is suitable for babies starting their very first mouthfuls of solids from 4 months onwards. We do however encourage you to start on the vegetable pack first, as like adults, babies naturally develop a love for sweet, however need to be trained to love the taste of vegetables. 
Each cube is a block of snap frozen, smooth puree designed to be heated (or served room temperature) and spoon fed to your infant. As your baby grows, matures and can tolerate more texture, you can start adding other elements to the puree such as unsweetened full fat greek yoghurt, oats or soaked chia seeds. Nourishing Bubs contain no additives, preservatives, flavours, thickeners or fillers and uses the most natural form of preservation without the need for harmful heat treatment. Our Baby's First Foods' Packs are designed to take the guesswork out of starting solids and lay healthy foundations for your baby from their very first mouthful, setting up healthy habits to last them a lifetime.
Each pack contains: 16 x 25g frozen cube portions of Pear, Plum, Strawberry and Apple. 4 x 25g frozen Pear cubes. 4 x 25g frozen Plum cubes. 4 x 25g frozen Strawberry cubes. 4 x 25g frozen Apple cubes.

Products.RichDescription:
WEIS ICE CREAM FRUITO 280 ML

Sweet pineapple, ripened bananas and tangy passionfruit topped with cream is how we made our first iconic bar ever - The Fruito Bar. It was developed by Cyril Weis in 1936 and first commercially sold by his son Les in 1957 - at Pop's Milk Bar across from the Empire Theatre in Toowoomba, Queensland. Based on the classic pairing of fruit salad and ice cream, the unique and refreshing taste and purity of ingredients remains a family favourite. It's the perfect treat for a hot summer's day! Fruit and cream are soulmates. Put them together with delicious natural ingredients, and you’ve got heaven in a Weis Bar. Our signature two-toned Classic Weis Bars, a moreish combination of real fruit and our traditional cream strip, are an irresistible indulgence – all wrapped up in a no stick, no-drip package. Available in a variety of flavours at your local snack bar, convenience store or service station. Or if you want to enjoy more of our divinely delicious Weis Bars, we’ve put them in Multipacks so you never have to run out. Look out for our colourful packs in the freezer at your supermarket. At Weis our products are based on recipes, so the focus is on the subtle blending of real ingredients and ultimately the taste. Our knowledge and expertise in sourcing and working with all different kinds of fruits, premium grade nuts and natural ingredients enables us to create unique combinations and taste experiences.

Sweet pineapple, ripened bananas, tangy passionfruit topped with cream is how we made our first iconic bar ever - The Fruito Bar.

Based on the simple concept of fruit salad and ice cream, the unique and refreshing taste and purity of ingredients remains a family favourite.

It's the perfect treat for a hot summer's day!

Products.SmallFormatDescription: Weis Ice Cream Mango & Cream
Products.FullDescription: Weis Ice Cream Mango & Cream
Products.RichDescription:
WEIS ICE CREAM MANGO 280 ML

How do we ensure every Weis mango is the best tasting mango available? Early every season, we meet with the mango farmers to check quality and crop size. Once those delicious Kensington Pride mangoes start arriving at Weis, it's all systems go. The mangoes are ripened in the warmth of the sun and checked daily to ensure they're processed at their peak. That's why the flavour in a Weis Mango bar is so unique, authentic, and perfectly balanced by a layer of traditional Weis ice cream. One bite and you're sure to be delighted. Fruit and cream are soulmates. Put them together with delicious natural ingredients, and you’ve got heaven in a Weis Bar. Our signature two-toned Classic Weis Bars, a moreish combination of real fruit and our traditional cream strip, are an irresistible indulgence – all wrapped up in a no stick, no-drip package. Available in a variety of flavours at your local snack bar, convenience store or service station. Or if you want to enjoy more of our divinely delicious Weis Bars, we’ve put them in Multipacks so you never have to run out. Look out for our colourful packs in the freezer at your supermarket. At Weis our products are based on recipes, so the focus is on the subtle blending of real ingredients and ultimately the taste. Our knowledge and expertise in sourcing and working with all different kinds of fruits, premium grade nuts and natural ingredients enables us to create unique combinations and taste experiences. Also try our Weis Ice Cream Macadamia Mango Cream 280ml, which includes macadamia nuts for that extra crunch.

This Mango ice cream bar is a summertime favourite that's made with real Kensington Pride mangoes and an ice cream strip.

Ice Cream made from real fruit and Australian dairy.

You can smell the freshness - picked at the farm, ripened under shade cloth at the Weis factory in Queensland and delivered to you as cool, creamy ice cream goodness.

No artificial colours or flavours

Gluten free ice cream

Ice cream made in Australia since 1957

Products.FullDescription: Weis Ice Cream Macadamia With Mango & Cream
Products.RichDescription:
WEIS ICE CREAM MACADAMIA MANGO CREAM 280 ML

It started with the nuts! At Weis we are pretty nutty about the quality of our ingredients and how they taste when we blend them together. That's why when we created the recipe for our Macadamia Mango Ice Cream Bar, the first thing we had to do was find the best tasting mango and roasted macadamias available. They were right on our doorstep on the Sunshine Coast Hinterland! The macadamias are cracked and then carefully cut into the right size chunks to complement our famous Weis ice cream and Australian Kensington Pride mangoes. We hope you are as nuts about the taste and texture as we are. Ice cream made from real fruit. Fruit and cream are soulmates. Put them together with delicious natural ingredients, and you’ve got heaven in a Weis Bar. Our signature two-toned Classic Weis Bars, a moreish combination of real fruit and our traditional cream strip, are an irresistible indulgence – all wrapped up in a no stick, no-drip package. Available in a variety of flavours at your local snack bar, convenience store or service station. Or if you want to enjoy more of our divinely delicious Weis Bars, we’ve put them in Multipacks so you never have to run out. Look out for our colourful packs in the freezer at your supermarket. At Weis, our knowledge and expertise in sourcing and working with all different kinds of fruits, premium grade nuts and natural ingredients enables us to create unique combinations and taste experiences.

This creamy ice cream mango bar is a summertime favourite that's made with real Kensington Pride mangoes.

Crunchy macadamia nuts sourced from the Sunshine Coast Hinterland!

Made with all Australian Dairy, Fruit & Nuts

Gluten free ice cream

No artificial colours or flavours

Ice cream made in Australia since 1957

Products.RichDescription: These sensational silken rice noodle rolls are a favourite in my family and on Yum Cha trolleys across Asia. Also known as Cheung Fun, the signature rolls are packed with plump whole prawns then drizzled with a lush light soy dressing. It?s the paper thin pastry and generous filling that makes for a truly authentic taste. Simply steam, slather in soy and let the feast begin.
